title: Adolf Hitler - Mein Kampf
description:
Thought this might be of interest to those curious about the workings of the  mind of one of the most infamous men in history.

Mein Kampf (English: My Struggle/My Battle) is a book by the Austrian-born leader of Nazi Germany, Adolf Hitler. It combines elements of autobiography with an exposition of Hitler's National Socialist political ideology. Volume 1 of Mein Kampf was published in 1925 and volume 2 in 1926.
